author: KEXP
description: Groove-laden gems float through @NoSoMusic's latest release 'When Are You Leaving?'. Through emotive vocals and gauzy synths, they demonstrate their artistic evolution with a performance of "Nara" and more Live on KEXP.
title: NoSo performs "Sugar" and more Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
